@startuml Deployment Diagram
!theme plain
title Sơ đồ Triển khai - Hệ thống Quản lý Ngân hàng

node ClientBrowser as "Client Browser" {
  artifact "React App" as ReactApp
}

node WebServer as "Web Server" {
  component "Nginx/Apache\n(Static Files)" as Nginx
  artifact "HTML/CSS/JS" as StaticFiles
}

node AppServer as "Application Server" {
  component "Node.js\nAPI Server" as NodeAPI
  note right
    - Express Framework
    - RESTful API
    - Business Logic
  end note
}

database DatabaseServer as "Database Server" {
  component "MySQL 8.0" as MySQL
  storage "Tables" as Tables
  note right
    - Customers, Accounts
    - Transactions, Loans
    - Savings, Credit Scores
  end note
}

' Connections
ClientBrowser --> Nginx : HTTPS Request
Nginx --> StaticFiles : Serve Files
ReactApp --> NodeAPI : API Calls (REST)
NodeAPI --> MySQL : SQL Queries
MySQL --> Tables : CRUD

note bottom of WebServer
  **Web Server:**
  - Port: 80/443
  - Serves React build
  - Static hosting
end note

note bottom of AppServer
  **App Server:**
  - Port: 3000/5000
  - Node.js Runtime
  - API Endpoints
end note

note bottom of DatabaseServer
  **Database:**
  - Port: 3306
  - InnoDB Engine
  - UTF8MB4 Charset
end note

@enduml
